metadata.name: Manifest
metadata.description:
-Manifest- 

Taken back in New Zealand I remember this moment vividly. I had just come back to New Zealand after studying in the states feeling lost and unsure of myself. After spending a year exploring around New Zealand with a camera in my hand i fell in love with capturing the beauty around me. 

From 2020 onwards i knew that photography was the passion I wanted to chase. Fast forward to now I made my dreams a reality as a full time photographer.
